<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Html To Node</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
  
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }
  
    p {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease;
    }
  
    p:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }
  
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  
    header {
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
  
    header nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    header nav a:hover {
      color: #f1c40f;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  
    button {
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    button:hover {
      background-color: #c0392b;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  </style>
  
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('head') %>

    <h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>
    <p>Create a multi-page web application with a frontend using EJS (Embedded JavaScript) for templating and a backend
      built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. The project should follow the MVC (Model-View-Controller) architecture.
    </p>
</body>

</html>